# RT Network — /ops must be a real, server-visible path (not a #hash) so
# Cloudflare Access can gate it at the edge without also blocking the
# client-facing /#plan or provider /#backstage/<token> links, which must
# stay reachable with no login. Everything else is pure client-side
# hash routing off the single index.html, so no other rules are needed.
/ops    /   200
/ops/*  /   200
